entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Ekirk's jobs have been completed to his satisfaction.  Enough information has been gathered for Dathnaeya to make a well informed decision regarding the Empire.
entries.journal_entry_description: All missions at the A.C.L.O. base have been completed.  All that is left is to report back to Galiir followed by Col. Ekirk.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The tasks assigned by Galiir Ac Yandar at the A.C.L.O. base are complete.  Report back to him in the Imperial Office in Dearic.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: All assigned tasks from Ekirk have been completed.  Return to him and receive the gratitude of the Empire.
